nodes.text: Joshua Max Brener (born October 1, 1984) is an American actor who voices Erskin Semaj in Star Wars Rebels and Neeku Vozo in Star Wars Resistance. He was known for playing Dale in The Big Bang Theory.
He is married to Meghan Falcone, who plays Nenavakasa Nalor in Star Wars Resistance.
